<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 03:34:09 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>中国誓言采取政策刺激措施，黄金涨幅扩大</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/gold-extends-gain-chinas-vow-policy-stimulus-2024-12-10/</link><description>周二金价延续涨势，主要消费国中国承诺加大政策刺激力度以帮助刺激经济增长，投资者等待美国通胀数据以进一步了解美联储的利率前景。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 03:27:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/gold-extends-gain-chinas-vow-policy-stimulus-2024-12-10/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾将继续在南海执行补给任务 不会导致局势升级</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-continue-resupply-missions-schina-sea-wont-escalate-situation-2024-12-10/</link><description>菲律宾总统小费迪南德·马科斯周二表示，尽管最近发生了与中国船只发生的事件，但该国将继续在南海执行补给任务，而无需部署海军。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 03:01:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-continue-resupply-missions-schina-sea-wont-escalate-situation-2024-12-10/</guid></item><item><title>台湾报告中国军用飞机和军舰在附近作业的数量激增</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-reports-surge-chinese-military-aircraft-ships-operating-nearby-2024-12-10/</link><description>台湾国防部报告称，周二中国在台湾周围的军事活动激增，其中包括 47 架军用飞机，台湾在总统结束美国之行回国后处于高度戒备状态。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 02:11:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-reports-surge-chinese-military-aircraft-ships-operating-nearby-2024-12-10/</guid></item><item><title>油价回落，但地缘政治风险和中国政策立场抑制损失</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/oil-prices-ease-geopolitical-risk-china-policy-stance-check-losses-2024-12-10/</link><description>周二，油价仅小幅回落，维持了前一交易日的大部分涨幅，原因是叙利亚总统巴沙尔·阿萨德倒台后地缘政治风险不断加大，而中国誓言加大政策刺激力度，使油价保持在底部。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 02:00:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/oil-prices-ease-geopolitical-risk-china-policy-stance-check-losses-2024-12-10/</guid></item><item><title>中国股市因政治局政策转变而上涨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-12-10/</link><description>周二，中国股市飙升，大宗商品和澳元因北京方面新的降息承诺和提振消费而获得支撑，而全球股市在关键的美国通胀数据公布之前出现波动。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 01:59:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-12-10/</guid></item><item><title>台美首个贸易倡议协议生效</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/first-agreement-under-taiwan-us-trade-initiative-come-into-force-2024-12-10/</link><description>两国政府宣布，台湾和美国根据贸易倡议签署的第一份协议将于周二生效，台北希望正在进行的一系列谈判最终能达成自由贸易协议。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 00:46:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/first-agreement-under-taiwan-us-trade-initiative-come-into-force-2024-12-10/</guid></item><item><title>美国各机构将向众议院通报中国盐台风电信黑客攻击事件</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/cybersecurity/us-agencies-brief-house-chinese-salt-typhoon-telecom-hacking-2024-12-09/</link><description>官员们周一表示，美国政府机构将于周二向众议院举行一次机密简报会，内容涉及中国所谓的“盐台风”渗透美国电信公司并窃取美国通话数据的行为。</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 22:14:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/cybersecurity/us-agencies-brief-house-chinese-salt-typhoon-telecom-hacking-2024-12-09/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：澳洲联储决定，中国政策转变引发争论</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-2024-12-09/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 21:53:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-2024-12-09/</guid></item><item><title>中国在伦敦新建大型大使馆的计划遭到当地官员拒绝</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-plans-large-new-london-embassy-rejected-by-local-officials-2024-12-09/</link><description>中国在伦敦设立新大型大使馆的计划周一被当地官员拒绝，理由是这可能对附近居民构成安全风险，这给中央政府带来了拒绝该规划申请的压力。</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 21:08:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-plans-large-new-london-embassy-rejected-by-local-officials-2024-12-09/</guid></item><item><title>国会可能禁止两家中国制造商生产新无人机</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/dji-could-be-banned-launching-new-products-us-under-proposed-bill-2024-12-09/</link><description>根据美国众议院将于本周晚些时候投票的年度军事法案，中国大疆创新和 Autel Robotics 可能被禁止在美国市场销售新无人机。</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 19:21:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/dji-could-be-banned-launching-new-products-us-under-proposed-bill-2024-12-09/</guid></item><item><title>币安首席执行官滕表示，币安仍在选择全球总部地点</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/binance-still-choose-location-global-headquarters-ceo-teng-says-2024-12-09/</link><description>加密货币交易所币安网首席执行官周一对路透表示，该公司尚未决定其全球总部的设立地点，此前该公司曾表示即将做出决定，但该高管指出了该公司为改善公司治理而采取的举措。</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 18:23:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/binance-still-choose-location-global-headquarters-ceo-teng-says-2024-12-09/</guid></item><item><title>法国欧安诺将与中国XTC成立两家合资企业</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/frances-orano-set-up-two-jvs-with-chinas-xtc-2024-12-09/</link><description>法国核电集团欧安诺周一宣布与中国XTC新能源材料集团成立两家合资企业，在法国敦刻尔克生产电动汽车电池组件。</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 17:53:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/frances-orano-set-up-two-jvs-with-chinas-xtc-2024-12-09/</guid></item><item><title>中国比亚迪在欧洲扩张中将重点关注插电式混合动力汽车</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-byd-focus-plug-in-hybrid-cars-european-expansion-2024-12-09/</link><description>中国电动汽车巨头比亚迪在欧洲的特别顾问周一表示，由于全电动汽车需求疲软，混合动力技术将成为该公司在欧洲扩张的关键。</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 15:54:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-byd-focus-plug-in-hybrid-cars-european-expansion-2024-12-09/</guid></item><item><title>在欧盟的中国企业表示，在全球紧张局势中，商业环境更加严峻</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/business-conditions-tougher-chinese-firms-eu-say-amid-global-tensions-2024-12-09/</link><description>周一公布的一项调查显示，在欧盟的中国企业表示，商业环境连续第五年恶化，地缘政治紧张局势加剧和反华情绪阻碍了运营。</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 14:27:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/business-conditions-tougher-chinese-firms-eu-say-amid-global-tensions-2024-12-09/</guid></item><item><title>字节跳动、TikTok 寻求暂时停止美国禁令，等待最高法院审查</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/legal/bytedance-tiktok-seek-temporary-halt-us-crackdown-law-pending-supreme-court-2024-12-09/</link><description>中国字节跳动及其短视频应用 TikTok 周一请求上诉法院暂时阻止一项法律，该法律要求母公司字节跳动在 1 月 19 日之前剥离 TikTok，否则将面临禁令，等待美国最高法院的审查。</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 14:21:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/legal/bytedance-tiktok-seek-temporary-halt-us-crackdown-law-pending-supreme-court-2024-12-09/</guid></item></channel></rss>